<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>把这些签纸放到什么里面去</b></font>

134
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:15,930
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>喂 去准备个袋子或者盒子什么的</b></font>

135
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:26,130
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>设局已经到了收尾阶段</b></font>

