<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哦 那个</b></font>

142
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>用那个吧</b></font>

143
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>切...</b></font>

144
