<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这个不行</b></font>

145
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:05,340
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>要用还没开封的新盒子</b></font>

146
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,010
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>会长</b></font>

147
00:09:07,610 --> 00:09:08,920
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>去拿就是了</b></font>

148
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:15,350
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>到此为止 都在按照开司的意料发展</b></font>

