00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:25,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只有这一点 是人力所无法操控的运气所决定的</b></font>

151
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:27,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果他拿小盒子来的话</b></font>

152
00:09:36,470 --> 00:09:37,140
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>成功了</b></font>

153
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:40,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这个行了吧</b></font>

