00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,840
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不过也不能完全排除动过手脚的可能性</b></font>

159
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:54,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你这混蛋 你这家伙到底要...</b></font>

160
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:55,260
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>让他看吧</b></font>

161
00:10:05,770 --> 00:10:07,020
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>做的太过火了吗</b></font>

162
00:10:07,730 --> 00:10:09,770
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可能反而引起会长怀疑了</b></font>

163
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:11,410
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>好了</b></font>

164
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:15,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你也确认一下吧</b></font>

165
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:18,720
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>为什么要做那种事</b></font>

166
00:10:19,250 --> 00:10:22,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这么做万一他看穿这圈套的话</b></font>

167
00:10:28,430 --> 00:10:30,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没问题</b></font>

168
00:10:33,090 --> 00:10:34,300
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>要开封了</b></font>

169
00:10:37,940 --> 00:10:39,870
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是吗 难道这也是...</b></font>

170
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:43,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这也是开司的策略</b></font>

171
00:10:43,890 --> 00:10:45,390
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果只有开司一个人检查</b></font>

172
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,900
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>确实可能因为该行为的不自然而引起怀疑</b></font>

173
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:50,650
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是也给对方检查的话</b></font>

174
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:54,990
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>比赛前的双方确认 会被当成是理所当然的行为</b></font>

175
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,410
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>而更为重要的是</b></font>

176
00:10:57,780 --> 00:11:00,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>要在开封之前让对方检查</b></font>

177
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:04,450
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>也就是说 在开了封把面纸抽出后再看盒子的话</b></font>

178
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:06,670
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>奖签就会被人看到</b></font>

179
00:11:07,210 --> 00:11:10,870
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>双方能检查的时机就只有开封前</b></font>

180
00:11:11,970 --> 00:11:16,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司首先通过自己检查盒子制造出理所当然的趋势</b></font>

181
00:11:16,810 --> 00:11:20,710
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>再将对方卷入其中 甚至令其说出没问题这样的话</b></font>

182
00:11:22,350 --> 00:11:25,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>太完美了 我甚至觉得震撼</b></font>

183
00:11:25,850 --> 00:11:30,650
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>人做事居然可以如此周到吗</b></font>

184
00:11:33,490 --> 00:11:34,090
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>放下吧</b></font>

185
00:11:41,570 --> 00:11:44,300
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>都准备好了 会长</b></font>

186
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,510
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这可不行啊</b></font>

187
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:03,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这可不行啊</b></font>

188
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:05,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>什么意思</b></font>

189
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:07,160
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>无趣</b></font>

190
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:10,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>费了那么多工夫却是如此单纯</b></font>

191
00:12:10,650 --> 00:12:15,700
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不是两个成年人强忍睡意在黎明时分该玩的游戏</b></font>

192
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:24,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>话虽如此 不过毕竟是给我带来那么多乐趣的开司你的请求</b></font>

193
00:12:24,850 --> 00:12:26,880
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我也没说不玩</b></font>

194
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:32,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是 如果要玩我有三个条件</b></font>

195
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:34,660
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>条件?</b></font>

196
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:37,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>也不是什么大不了的事</b></font>

197
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:39,890
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你听了后就会觉得理所当然了</b></font>

198
00:12:39,930 --> 00:12:43,180
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>都是开司你可以理解的条件</b></font>

199
00:12:44,730 --> 00:12:45,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你说说看</b></font>

200
00:12:47,170 --> 00:12:48,870
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>第一个条件</b></font>

201
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:54,040
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是关于认定奖签的 为了防止作弊</b></font>

202
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,850
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>防止作弊?</b></font>

203
00:12:56,210 --> 00:12:57,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你好好看看</b></font>

204
00:12:58,160 --> 00:13:02,080
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这个掌握着我们的命运的奖签是如此单薄</b></font>

205
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>简直是风吹就倒</b></font>

206
00:13:04,700 --> 00:13:07,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>所以我们必须做一些保护工作</b></font>

207
00:13:08,630 --> 00:13:11,660
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>首先第一条是 禁止揉成团</b></font>

208
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:12,600
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哎?</b></font>

209
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:16,800
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这种东西揉成团的话 别说是手指间</b></font>

210
00:13:16,930 --> 00:13:18,840
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>甚至能藏在指甲里</b></font>

211
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:25,480
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>所以 我们就不承认这种被揉成团的奖签吧</b></font>

212
00:13:27,540 --> 00:13:29,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果承认这样的签的话</b></font>

213
00:13:29,150 --> 00:13:30,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>也许有人会装成在抽签</b></font>

214
00:13:30,250 --> 00:13:38,090
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>其实却抽出了预先藏在头发里或是耳朵里的签来假冒奖签</b></font>

215
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:39,790
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你明白吗</b></font>

216
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:41,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>原来如此</b></font>

217
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我同意</b></font>

218
00:13:43,130 --> 00:13:44,290
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不允许揉成团</b></font>

219
00:13:46,260 --> 00:13:47,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果要再加一条的话</b></font>

220
00:13:47,530 --> 00:13:50,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>在抽签时当然应该卷起袖子</b></font>

221
00:13:50,370 --> 00:13:55,910
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>并且在要抽之前互相检查手指间歇 确认手掌别无他物</b></font>

222
00:13:56,470 --> 00:13:57,670
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没意见吧</b></font>

223
00:13:58,840 --> 00:13:59,340
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯</b></font>

224
00:14:01,340 --> 00:14:03,410
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那么第二个条件</b></font>

225
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:07,620
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这个条件有些厚脸皮了</b></font>

226
00:14:08,190 --> 00:14:11,020
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我希望你让我先抽</b></font>

227
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:12,770
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>什么?</b></font>

228
00:14:13,570 --> 00:14:19,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就是说 第一次抽签的权力给我 我希望你答应</b></font>

229
00:14:20,410 --> 00:14:21,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这怎么行</b></font>

230
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:25,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这种事情一般不是应该公平地通过猜拳来决定吗</b></font>

231
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,440
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>说的有理</b></font>

232
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:33,790
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是这一次我一直以来都是全盘接受了开司的要求</b></font>

233
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:39,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>按他的要求接受比赛 并且接受了他准备的抽签游戏</b></font>

234
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:43,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我真是个惊天地泣鬼神的好人啊</b></font>

235
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:47,600
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>尽管如此 虽说几率很渺小</b></font>

236
00:14:47,640 --> 00:14:51,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但万一开司第一手就抽中的话</b></font>

237
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:57,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我甚至连抽签的机会都没有 比赛就结束了</b></font>

238
00:14:58,540 --> 00:15:01,950
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这不是也太过分了点吗</b></font>

239
00:15:02,450 --> 00:15:05,950
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只有这种情况我必须避免啊 无论如何都想避免</b></font>

240
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:08,660
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司</b></font>

241
00:15:10,210 --> 00:15:13,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果你不愿意的话 我就不玩了</b></font>

242
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:16,890
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可恶</b></font>

243
00:15:17,290 --> 00:15:18,840
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>明知道我就怕弃权</b></font>

244
00:15:20,050 --> 00:15:23,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不过本来也不见得就是我先抽</b></font>

245
00:15:24,050 --> 00:15:25,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果只是一次的话...</b></font>

246
00:15:27,430 --> 00:15:28,390
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>随你便吧</b></font>

247
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司</b></font>

248
00:15:30,930 --> 00:15:33,340
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>感谢你的理解支持</b></font>

249
00:15:33,940 --> 00:15:37,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那么 第三个 也是最后的条件</b></font>

